      "html": "<div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γναΐου Μοδίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γναΐου\"><span data-text=\"Γναΐου\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">Γναΐου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Μοδίου\"><span data-text=\"Μοδίου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">Μοδίου</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γναΐου Μοδίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γναΐου\"><span data-text=\"Γναΐου\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"\">ΓΝΑΙΟΥ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Μοδίου\"><span data-text=\"Μοδίου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"\">ΜΟΔΙΟΥ</span></span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
